hopobject.body: What's the current interest rate for personal loans? medicdirectshop.eu Central London or "prime London" are classed as those neighbourhoods around Hyde Park including Kensington, Mayfair and Knightsbridge. Here there has long been activity by foreign buyers. Knight Frank's research found 49pc of buyers in these areas were non-UK by nationality. When it came to buyers' country of residence, however, the majority - 72pc - lived here.
